    "Table 1 displays how many times each metric was used to evaluate summaries in the reviewed papers.",
    "The ROUGE score is the most extensively used.",
    "On a positive note, 7/17 of the papers perform some form of human evaluation, while BERT/BARTScore and BLEU metrics are also used.",
    "Text summarization datasets typically consist of pairs of source documents and their corresponding reference summaries, covering domains such as news articles, scientific papers, Wikipedia articles.",
